name: T4 Reusable Check
on:
  workflow_call:
    inputs:
      branch-name:
        required: true
        type: string
jobs:
  verify:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
        with:
          ref: ${{ inputs["branch-name"] }}
      - uses: pnpm/action-setup@v3
        with:
          version: 9
      - uses: actions/setup-node@v4
        with:
          node-version: 20
      - run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
      - run: pnpm -r build
      - run: pnpm tf:check
      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: tf-check-${{ inputs["branch-name"] }}
          path: out/t2/tf-check

template.description: Dual-stack template for evaluating parallel TS and Rust branches
template.name: dual-stack
